Rating: 4
made this recipe as an entree dish and it was so yummy! The full recipe (3 lbs. of clams) is enough for 2 full entree size servings. I would eliminate adding any salt though, as the clams add enough saltiness to the dish. Skipped the breadcrumbs. Instead, I just added the lemon zest at the end. The lemon zest added a brightness to the dish. This one is a keeper!

Rating: 4
I used larger, hard shelled clams for the recipe - more to eat, with less effort at the end. It was amazingly tasty and superbly easy to prepare. The flavor was absorbed very well. Everyone loved them - a definite keeper.

