Rating: 4
Wonderful dish!! I had to use dried oregano, but it was fine. Instead of the plum tomatoes, I used a small can of Fire Roasted Tomatoes (Muir Glen) and also added about 1/2 c. white wine when I added the clams. I actually forgot the bread crumbs and did not realize it until the meal was over. So, guess you could say they were not missed! We loved this recipe and will make often!

