Rating: 4
Excellent dish! To round out the meal, I sauteed some red peppers, onions, garlic and mushrooms in olive oil and tossed them with some cooked vermicelli and some of the broth from the clam dish, served the clams on top and sprinkled the bread crumbs over all of it.

Rating: 4
Great, easy recipe with a lot of punch! Used larger cherrystone clams, added white wine to sauce and reduced. Also added more veggies--bell peppers, onions and lots of mushrooms. Bread crumbs added a nice texture to the sauce. Would definitely try this with other shellfish. mmm!!

